          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Merit Systems Protection Board Reauthorization Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes the Merit Systems Protection Board (MSPB) for FY2019-FY2023. Additionally, the bill modifies the authority of the MSPB and directs it to establish a filing fee for claims.</p>]]></text>
